16:T54b,Tracy is soul guide and mentor, energetic interpreter, and international facilitator based on the Kohala Coast. She is given to empowering souls deeply landed in matter and honoring the multitude of realities and expressions of love within each of us. Tracy has spent the last decade immersed in both study and practice within traditions of healing and integration, energetic mastery, and soul initiation. She combines lived experience, years of training and depth of study with intuitive adeptness and precise energetic attunement in her work. 

Tracy's soul mentorship is focused on midwifing souls into embodied depth and well being.  Her one on one practice welcomes individuals and couples and covers the following:
-Emotional fluency
-Nervous system regulation and stabilization
-Neuroplasticity training
-Relational wellness
-Erotic embodiment
-Practical integration for soulful living
-Clearing patterns and behaviors that inhibit wellness and radiance

Tracy's group work focuses on supporting fields of vibratory coherence between humans and building group capacity for generative healing , creativity, and collaboration. This work is deeply supportive for organizations, collectives, and any group wanting to understand relational dynamics to support generative and resourcing environments. Reach out directly to find out more about group work.14:["$","$L15",null,{"islandSlug":"big-island","islandDisplayName":"Big Island","modalitySlug":"breathwork","modalityName":"Breathwork","practitioners":[{"id":"63c17020-1b66-480a-8bc5-eb80d7ed5ef9","name":"Somatic Therapy","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/practitioners/1774573523320-uz5q8ciqyir.webp","type":"practitioner","modality":"Somatic Therapy, Breathwork, Trauma-Informed Care, Soul Guidance, Nervous System Regulation, Meditation, Craniosacral, Energy Healing","modalities":["Somatic Therapy","Breathwork","Trauma-Informed Care","Soul Guidance","Nervous System Regulation","Meditation","Craniosacral","Energy Healing"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Somatic Therapy, Somatic Experiencing, IFS Internal Family Systems, Akashic Records Readings, Somatic Bodywork, CranialSacral, Past Life Regression in South Kona online and in-person.","location":"Captain Cook","rating":5,"lat":19.420526,"lng":-155.884115,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"$undefined","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:41.456979+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"c85f0fc9-5103-4747-a76f-56065357fc64","name":"Jackie Orsa","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/fde082bd3e3c74f5b5d18698f4150534.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Breathwork, Yoga, Nervous System Regulation","modalities":["Breathwork","Yoga","Nervous System Regulation"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"As a certified yoga teacher and a yoga therapist in training, I work with individuals and small groups, both in person and virtually, offering supportive, personalized practices for those navigating symptoms of stress, anxiety, and overwhelm.","location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"$undefined","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:40.532049+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"eb2a3653-8642-40e1-a65a-039506839d6c","name":"Michelle Kuroda, LAc Acupuncture | Dry Needling | Lifestyle Medicine","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/63c747b05df89327236c6b78/t/6931a01e82dbf766ed2099d7/1764859934439/MKLogoLeafround.png?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Acupuncture, Nervous System Regulation, Breathwork","modalities":["Acupuncture","Nervous System Regulation","Breathwork"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Michelle Kuroda, LAc, is a master acupuncturist offering a refined, whole-person approach to healing and transformation. Through acupuncture, dry needling, breathwork, nervous system regulation, and lifestyle design, she supports resilience, clarity, vitality, and embodied presence for those seeking","location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.626484,"lng":-155.98639,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:57:40.368069+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"994d3f4a-3781-43aa-ac49-944d275414a3","name":"Pam Neil","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"https://sccksxvjckllxlvyuotv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/practitioner-images/09ef9f406844ac089917390754b11796.jpg","type":"practitioner","modality":"Breathwork, Reiki","modalities":["Breathwork","Reiki"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"It’s Pam’s passion to facilitate those who want to create a more peaceful, balanced, easy life of love and joy one breath at a time. She combines Healing Touch with Conscious Breathwork, guiding her clients to relax in both mind and body. These two healing modalities strengthen and support the immune system, balance the energy and increase the prana, or life force. Working with the breath is a powerful and proven method to restore your nervous system, energize you when tired, increase your focus","location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"b4036191-25ff-432c-9aad-a7ea1432aba4","name":"Pati Hoyt","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/6064dbd8e8dbb42926b2929a/t/65a819090631410578346af6/1705515273997/Prancheta+3%404x.png?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Breathwork, Soul Guidance","modalities":["Breathwork","Soul Guidance"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Explore retreats and healing experiences with Pati Hoyt to reconnect, heal, and elevate your spiritual journey. Discover personalized wellness offerings now.","location":"Keaau","rating":5,"lat":19.610017,"lng":-154.950551,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"5550a7b5-8614-499d-8fe8-248fbca881b7","name":"Hypnotherapy in Kona, Hawaii & online","title":"$undefined","businessName":"$undefined","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/56d7004986db43480aa1bcc3/t/698126e3cf62b0699d1b3b6a/1770071779617/social-logo.jpg?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Breathwork, Psychotherapy, hypnotherapy, Hypnotherapy","modalities":["Breathwork","Psychotherapy","hypnotherapy","Hypnotherapy"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Struggling with anxiety? Discover how hypnotherapy, breathwork & coaching \ncan release anxiety patterns at the root. Feel calm & in control again. \nBook now.","locati